---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="customers" title="From nightly phone calls to live business control." lead="This is the transformation PumpOS is designed to create. Real customer stories will replace this benchmark once deployments mature.">
  <div class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] bg-white p-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#9B2C20]">Before PumpOS</p>
      <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em]">Three hours to close a shift.</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">Manual registers, Excel totals, WhatsApp updates, and a manager call at the end of every day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] bg-white p-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand)]">After PumpOS</p>
      <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em]">Twenty minutes, with numbers the owner can trust.</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">Shift close, stock movement, ledgers, DSSR, and owner dashboard all update from the same operational record.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
